      {
        "hadithnumber": 1528,
        "arabicnumber": 1528,
        "text": "Narrated 'Uqbah bin 'Amir:That the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: \"The atonement of a vow when it is not specified is the atonement of an oath",
