        "arabicnumber": 1531,
        "text": "Narrated Ibn 'Umar:That the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: \"Whoever swears about an oath and says: 'If Allah wills (Insha Allah), then there is no breaking of the oath against him",
        "grades": [
          {
            "name": "Ahmad Muhammad Shakir",
            "grade": "Sahih"
