        "arabicnumber": 1532,
        "text": "Narrated Abu Hurairah:That the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: \"Whoever swears [about an oath] and says: 'If Allah wills (Insha Allah), then he will not have broken it",
        "grades": [
          {
            "name": "Ahmad Muhammad Shakir",
