      {
        "hadithnumber": 1533,
        "arabicnumber": 1533,
        "text": "Narrated Salim:From his father (Ibn 'Umar) that the Prophet (ﷺ) heard 'Umar saying: \"By my father, By my father!\" So he said: \"Verily Allah prohibits you from swearing by your father.\" So 'Umar said: \"By Allah I did not swear by him after that, neither intentionally nor in narrating",
        "grades": [
          {
            "name": "Ahmad Muhammad Shakir",
            "grade": "Sahih"
          },
          {
            "name": "Al-Albani",
            "grade": "Sahih"
