      },
      {
        "hadithnumber": 1535,
        "arabicnumber": 1535,
        "text": "Narrated Sa'd bin 'Ubaidah:That Ibn 'Umar heard a man saying: \"No by the Ka'bah\" so Ibn 'Umar said: \"Nothing is sworn by other than Allah, for I heard the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) say: 'Whoever swears by other than Allah, he has committed disbelief or shirk",
        "grades": [
          {
            "name": "Ahmad Muhammad Shakir",
            "grade": "Sahih"
