      },
      {
        "hadithnumber": 1536,
        "arabicnumber": 1536,
        "text": "Narrated Anas:\"A Woman vowed to walk to the House of Allah, so the Prophet (ﷺ) asked about that, and he said: 'Verily Allah is in no need of her walking, order her to ride",
