      {
        "hadithnumber": 1538,
        "arabicnumber": 1538,
        "text": "Narrated Abu Hurairah:That the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: \"Do not vow, for the vows does not prevent what is decreed at all, and it only causes the miser to spend (of his wealth)",
